                          dpmi setup keep cwsdpmi.exe beside protected-mode programs need host                                                                                            DPMI setup                                                      Keep CWSDPMI.EXE beside protected-mode programs that need a DPMI host.                                                                                                                          batch safety check exist before running large files print clear status lines step                                                                               Batch safety                                                    Check IF EXIST before running large files and print clear status lines for each step.                                                                                                           path setup put program directories only needed keep command line short                                                                                          PATH setup                                                      Put program directories in PATH only when needed, and keep the command line short.                                                                                                              config sys config.sys tuning himem.sys dos high umb modest files buffers values compatibility                                                                   CONFIG.SYS tuning                                               Use HIMEM.SYS, DOS=HIGH,UMB, and modest FILES and BUFFERS values for compatibility.                                                                                                             hardware validation run same batch path real dos copy return.txt back compare checksums logs                                                                    Hardware validation                                             Run the same batch path on real DOS, copy RETURN.TXT back, and compare checksums and logs.                                                                                                      checksums dos sha-256 sidecars host compare file sizes checksum tool unavailable                                                                                DOS checksums                                                   Use SHA-256 sidecars on the host and compare file sizes on DOS when a checksum tool is unavailable.                                                                                             